{
  "texts": [
    "Zhang et al.",
    "29 used a support vector machine with naive Bayes features to optimize CNNs and improve the accuracy of sentiment classification.",
    "Phan et al.",
    "30 proposed a fuzzy-enhanced deep neural network (FeDN2), which deepens deep neural networks by adding fuzzy and defuzzy classes to improve sentence-level sentiment analysis.",
    "Recently, coarse-grained sentiment analysis has undergone a shift toward large pretrained language models (e.g., BERT, RoBERTa and XLNet) 31."
  ]
}